'init-method' & 'destroy-method'
-----------------------------------------------------------52

    #   Can be used for XML based configuration
    
    #   Example
        +   <bean id="foo"  class="com.wiley.beginningspring.ch2.Foo"
                        init-method="init" destroy-method="destroy"/>
                        
